column1: **Please note: empty cells representing half-hourly consumption mean that there is no data available for that time; numbers followed by an 'E' are unreliable numbers

**please NOTE: for the period 20th February, 04:00 - 29th March 2011, 10:00 only hourly consumption is available, resulting in a number for the full hour representing the total for this hour, followed by a zero of the half hour
Please NOTE: due to a disconnection issue there is no data available for the time period 2011-03-29 10:30 - 2011-03-31 17:00
